txt.en: 'What interesting things you have brought me! I look forward to learning what I can about them. Thank you for keeping them out of the hands of those who would not appreciate them for their history and artistry. You have my thanks.'
Narnien is in Gaerond, in the northern Angle.\n\nYou should bring the ancient artifacts to Narnien.
